elements.name: pageMargins
comments: [left, top, right, bottom] or [horizontal, vertical] or just a number for equal margins

elements.name: fontSize
comments: number: size of the font in pt

elements.name: fontFeatures
comments: string[]: array of advanced typographic features supported in TTF fonts (supported features depend on font file)

elements.name: alignment
comments: string: (‘left’ or ‘center’ or ‘right’) the alignment of the text

elements.name: characterSpacing
comments: number: size of the letter spacing in pt

elements.name: color
comments: string: the color of the text (color name e.g., ‘blue’ or hexadecimal color e.g., ‘#ff5500’)

elements.name: background
comments: string the background color of the text

elements.name: markerColor
comments: string: the color of the bullets in a buletted list

elements.name: decoration
comments: string: the text decoration to apply (‘underline’ or ‘lineThrough’ or ‘overline’)

elements.name: decorationStyle
comments: string: the style of the text decoration (‘dashed’ or ‘dotted’ or ‘double’ or ‘wavy’)
